DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
     The ppi interface provides a means of communication with
     HP-IB printers and plotters.

     Special files _p_p_i_0 through _p_p_i_7 are used to access the dev-
     ices, with the digit at the end of the filename referring to
     the bus address of the device.  Current versions of the
     autoconf code can not probe for these devices, so the device
     entry in the configuration file must be fully qualified.

